FULL PROJECT PROPOSAL
Title:
Basic Unit Converter
I. Problem
People often need to convert units in school, cooking, travel, and other activities. Manual conversions can be slow and confusing, especially when formulas are involved.
II. Target Users
Students, teachers, and anyone who needs fast and accurate conversions.
III. Objectives
Provide a simple and beginner-friendly converter


Allow users to convert different types of units


Make conversions fast and accurate


Create a clear menu to guide the user


IV. Key Features
Convert Length units


Convert Weight units


Convert Temperature units


Input validation to avoid errors


V. Expected Inputs
Value to convert (number)


Conversion type selected


VI. Expected Outputs
Converted value


A message showing what the value was converted from and to
VIII. Expected Outcome
A working unit converter that helps users easily convert measurements without manual formulas.
